CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773252369
OL,3,C'Absolutely no faith' in Irish
OL,4,CGovernment providing answers in Omagh
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the DUP Leader Gavin
OL,8,FRobinson has said a "political spat"
OL,9,Fbetween the UK and Irish Governments
OL,10,Fmeans that the Gardai has never shared
OL,11,Fany information with the commission
OL,12,Fwhich was set up to investigate legacy
OL,13,Fcases here.
OL,15,F16-year-old Alan Radford was one of
OL,16,Fthe 29 people, as well as unborn
OL,17,Ftwins, who were killed in Omagh in
OL,18,FAugust 1998.
OL,20,FClaire told the Omagh Bombing Inquiry
OL,21,Fabout him during hearings in 2025.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773252369
OL,3,C'Absolutely no faith' in Irish
OL,4,CGovernment providing answers in Omagh
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FClaire Hayes said: "There was never an
OL,8,FAlan without a Claire, or a Claire
OL,9,Fwithout an Alan."
OL,11,FWhile the bomb inquiry set up by the
OL,12,FUK Government has been hearing
OL,13,Fevidence, families of those killed
OL,14,Falso want the Irish Government to do
OL,15,Fmore to provide answers to what it
OL,16,Fcould have done to prevent the
OL,17,Fatrocity, through its own inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
