PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773252369
OL,3,C'Absolutely no faith' in Irish
OL,4,CGovernment providing answers in Omagh
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the DUP leader Gavin
OL,8,FRobinson has said the Garda is not
OL,9,Fsharing information with the
OL,10,FIndependent Commission for
OL,11,FReconciliation and Information
OL,12,FRecovery`the body set up to
OL,13,Finvestigate legacy cases.
OL,15,FHe also said the Irish government
OL,16,Fneeds to do more.
OL,18,FGavin Robinson said: "That's a
OL,19,Fpolitical spat between them and our
OL,20,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
