OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773252369
OL,3,C'Absolutely no faith' in Irish
OL,4,CGovernment providing answers in Omagh
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,F"That's not a spat with any victims
OL,8,Finvolved in.
OL,10,F"The victims are able to go to the
OL,11,FOmagh inquiry in Omagh and hear about
OL,12,Fwhat UK authorities may or may not
OL,13,Fhave been able to do to prevent the
OL,14,Fattack.
OL,16,F"They can understand nothing about
OL,17,Fwhat the Irish government could have
OL,18,Fdone to prevent the attack."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
