PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773252369
OL,3,C'Absolutely no faith' in Irish
OL,4,CGovernment providing answers in Omagh
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FBoth governments agreed the legacy
OL,8,Fframework in 2025 to make changes to
OL,9,Fwhat is currently in place on legacy,
OL,10,Fbut it has not gone through
OL,11,FWestminster yet and that is what the
OL,12,FIrish government appears to be waiting
OL,13,Ffor.
OL,15,FIrish Foreign Affairs Minister, Helen
OL,16,FMcEntee TD said: "There have been
OL,17,Frulings and there's a particular view
OL,18,Fthat this in itself is not ECHR
OL,19,Fcompliant.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
