OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1773252369
OL,3,C'Absolutely no faith' in Irish
OL,4,CGovernment providing answers in Omagh
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,F"And so there's obviously work being
OL,8,Fdone to ensure that when we get to a
OL,9,Fpoint through the Commission where we
OL,10,Fare able to, and the Garda are able to
OL,11,Fengage, that that will be the case."
OL,13,FIn a statement, the ICRIR said: "It is
OL,14,Fa matter for both governments to
OL,15,Faddress any outstanding issues around
OL,16,Finformation sharing."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
