OL,3,C'Absolutely no faith' in Irish
OL,4,CGovernment providing answers in Omagh
OL,5,CInquiry
OL,7,FThe next stage of the government's
OL,8,Flegacy legislation is expected by the
OL,9,Fend of March, and discussions between
OL,10,Fthe two governments are set to
OL,11,Fcontinue.
